::Rodimus Prime/Kup ::

As the power goes out and emergency lighting goes on Rodimus and Kup both draw their weapons from subspace.

Rodimus: What else could go wrong? Perseus, will you need any aid? I&#39;m with Kup, Windlord and Nightlight.

Kup: We try to find out about any trouble elsewhere on the planet and find a damn jamming field over this city and then lose all power. Someone is screwing with us... Wait, dowe have any prisoners? The brig systems would be down.

Kraftlos &lt;kraftlos@...&gt; wrote:                                  Lord Perseus&#39; CR beeps and the door opens.  He was about to ask for a
 status update when he heard the conversation on com pannel.

 Meanwhile...

 The scan came through.  This time he had used a passive scan and
 brought another, more-powerful scanning station online.

 &quot;We are detecting a decepticon signal as well as predecon and maximal.
  We are having trouble getting a read on.... hold on.&quot;

 Salveo looked at the radar and saw that he was unable to see anything
 in Atlantis.

 &quot;It looks like some kind of jamming field near the base.  Let me run
 another scan.&quot;

 &quot;Jamming, what is the source?&quot; Perseus finally asked.

 Just then the light went off and the reactor made a loud powering down sound.

 &quot;That isnt good...&quot; stated Salveo.

 The auxiliary power came on and the base was lit with a dim red light.

 &quot;I&#39;m going to go check on the reactor.  Get a status report from all
 stations.&quot; said Perseus.

 Meanwhile...

 Trelos was startled by the sound of the power shutting off.  But
 immediately saw his way out.

 &quot;Trelos... terrorize!&quot;

 Grabbing the bars with both hands, which were no longer protected by
 the forcefield, he bent them aside and stepped out of his cell.

 The security guard, who was behind the safety glass, reached for the
 com pannel.  Trelos blasted the guard through the glass, knocking him
 down neutralizing him.  Trelos sparked and flinched for a moment.

 &quot;You can stay here if you like,&quot; said Trelos to Blacknightmare, &quot;I&#39;m
 getting out of here.&quot;

